Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.01,0:00:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Shinsuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang kembali\Ndari skors panjangmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Skors hanyalah liburan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia ini masih busuk seperti biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak hukum atau peraturan bodoh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang terus memburuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat keberatan dengan amendemen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ordonansi Pengembangan Pemuda Sehat
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di Kabukicho.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, dengan penampilan ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kurasa itu akan menyegarkan\Ningatan pemirsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menghilanglah dengan ingatanku\Nsalah mengira kau Pak Shinsuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau masih sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Shinsuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat kejam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Giliran kita untuk memiliki korban.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Toushi, kau sudah menyelidikinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Semua orang menyebut ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Keributan Stiker".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka menjual stiker dengan kata "Sangat Jahat"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}masing-masing seharga puluhan ribu yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ada yang berani menolak,\Nmereka memakai taktik penjualan kasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini taktik umum\Ndi antara para berandal dunia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang buruk kali ini
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah identitas pelakunya\Nbenar-benar tersembunyi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa sudah waktunya\NKomite Disiplin turun tangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kabar buruk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ta…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takasugi benar-benar datang ke sekolah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa Takasugi ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bahkan tidak ingat\Nnama teman sekelasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu penuaan prematur?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat, Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, Takasugi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}langsung diskors dari sekolah\Nsejak semester baru dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu latarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tae, tolong jangan gunakan\Nistilah terang-terangan seperti "latar".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shinsuke Takasugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak SMA Gintama didirikan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia dikenal sebagai berandal\Npaling menakutkan, paling kejam,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan terkuat di Kelas 3-Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Zura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah sudah jelas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau ke toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katsura punya
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}punya hubungan mendalam dengan Takasugi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang lebih dalam dari laut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisakah kau membicarakan\Nmasa lalu bocah edgelord di luar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Catherine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}semua orang juga begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selalu ada satu atau dua masa lalu\Nyang orang tidak ingin sebutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu masa lalu dari sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan bagian ini\Nbukan hanya sebelum skorsnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini cerita dari sebelum\Nanime "GINTAMA" berakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimanapun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kuharap itu tidak menyebabkan keributan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takasugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beraninya kau memaksa anak buah kami\Nmembeli barang norak seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami tahu betul\Nini perbuatan faksi Takasugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berengsek!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Shinsuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus bergegas membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, siapa mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- SMA Gintama\N- Takasugi, katakan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- memiliki fraksi berandal yang berbeda\N- Jangan meremehkan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- dari Takasugi,\N- Itulah
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- yang menjadi saingannya sebelum diskors.\N- yang tidak kusukai darimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Itu latarnya.\N- Kau mendengarkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhenti menggunakan kata "latar", ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Para berandal itu bilang,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Kenapa Ginpachi pakai awal Episode 3\Nuntuk menyiapkan kemunculan Takasugi?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Ini upaya menyenangkan penggemar\Ndan menjual lebih banyak Blu-ray?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah mereka mulai bertengkar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tapi siapa yang kau hina?\N- Rasakan ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Matilah, Takasugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shin, aku membeli roti kroket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau memukuli orang dengan roti?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk menghadapi pria dengan niat membunuh,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}roti kroket panas memang yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permainan kata itu sama sekali tidak lucu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kroket hari ini lebih besar dari biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menemukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Ketsuno dari Klub Siaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau Shinsuke Takasugi dari Kelas 3-Z, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa diwawancarai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Klub Penyiaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa mereka mengincar Pak Shinsuke
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk berita eksklusif?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika dia terekspos
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berkelahi begitu kembali ke sekolah…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menghancurkan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berita eksklusif mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lupakan soal menghancurkan\Nberita eksklusif,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu malah menjadi gelar wicara misterius.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kubilang jangan wawancarai Shinsuke\Ndan masukkan dia ke gelar wicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka setuju tanpa ragu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya, kau memberi mereka\Nsituasi yang lebih menguntungkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya Klub Siaran
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak sadar mereka melewatkan\Npeluang berita eksklusif.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau harus sadar bahwa kau sudah gila!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, hari ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami mengundang berandal paling kejam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan paling menakutkan sejak pendirian
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}SMA Gintama, Shinsuke Takasugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita pasti akan memaksanya\Nmengungkap sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin Pak Shinsuke\Nakan mengungkap apa pun di acara ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di anime lama "GINTAMA",
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau tidak punya banyak adegan lucu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi, sulit untuk menyesuaikan diri\Nkarena temanya komedi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya kau diskors. Soal itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ungkap sesuatu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak menduga pewawancara\Nakan mengungkap sesuatu lebih dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kudengar untuk membuat kehebohan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk anime "Ginpachi" di episode 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}skorsmu tiba-tiba dicabut.\NBisa ceritakan perasaanmu sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini lebih dari sekadar pengungkapan.\NIni kebocoran internal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa ungkapkan perasaanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dilihat dari ini, kurasa\NPak Shinsuke tidak akan menjawab.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang saatnya pedang dihunus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sekolah tempat semua orang puas\Ndengan status quo ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku memikirkan cara\Nmengambil langkah pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menghunus pedang? Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tidak mengatakan hal seperti itu\Ndengan santai dalam hidup,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Shinsuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, itu terlalu sulit dimengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa jelaskan dengan lebih sederhana?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa dengan wanita itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menghunus pedang dan semacamnya
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memang sulit dimengerti,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia tidak sopan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang bisa kembali ke sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu terlalu terus terang, Pak Shinsuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menghargainya jika kau bisa\Nmemberikan sentimen yang lebih dalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau ingin yang dalam,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bagaimana jika aku menguburmu\Ndi dasar Teluk Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang anime ini kembali tayang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Shinsuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sungguh tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum wanita itu tenggelam ke dasar laut,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}popularitas Pak Shinsuke\Nmungkin akan tenggelam lebih cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bilang anime ini kembali tayang?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sebenarnya, itu spin-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada dasarnya, itu perspektif berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perspektif berbeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Acara ini tidak sedetail itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa menyebutnya "reboot", bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita hanya bisa terus berjuang\Ndalam perspektif ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu naik!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Muncul dari dasar laut!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah Pak Shinsuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya. Pintar sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apakah topik hangat saat ini\N"Keributan Stiker"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}juga bagian dari "perjuangan"\Nyang kau sebutkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terus mengobrol,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi sepertinya waktu kita habis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takasugi, terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, tolong jawab\Nsatu pertanyaan terakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menggunakan "anime" sebagai analogi…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa ada tebak-tebakan di akhir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anime "Ginpachi" saja
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak bisa meminta Pak Shinsuke\Nmelakukan ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menggunakan "anime" sebagai analogi…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sungguh melakukan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Inikah jalan yang ingin diambil\NPak Shinsuke dari "Ginpachi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini seperti meminta\Nbungkus hadiah di kasir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kesamaan mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menantikan pembukaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Sugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Shinsuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya, kelas kita pun punya korban?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Berapa lama kau akan menangis?\N- Keributan ini
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kendalikan dirimu.\N- di sekolah adalah ulah Takasugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi keributan ini terjadi\Njauh sebelum Takasugi diskors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak mungkin Takasugi terlibat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka lebih merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada berandal yang memeras orang\Ndi wilayah mereka sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pikir Takasugi akan diam saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengenal sifatnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sudah jelas dia akan manfaatkan keributan\Nuntuk membuat kekacauan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Lalu seluruh sekolah akan terpengaruh.\N- Kudengar Takasugi kembali ke sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shinpachi, kau mau ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku murid piket hari ini,\Njadi, aku akan menyerahkan jurnalnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Sakata… dimohon datang\Nke Kantor Kepala Sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kantor Kepala Sekolah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku penasaran apa rencana Pak Shinsuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia meminta kita\Nmenyelidiki Keributan Stiker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tidak bisa memahami ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi apa kau sudah lupa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan Shinsuke yang lama…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu dia melihat api yang berkedip,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia akan menuangkan minyak mendidih
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan mengubahnya menjadi api neraka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah dia pria seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,\Nsekolah sepertinya juga bertindak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang mereka rencanakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa mereka mengirim guru\Nuntuk menyelidiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keadaan akhirnya menjadi menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keributan Stiker?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keributan ini terjadi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}begitu Takasugi di kelasmu\Nkembali ke sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah itu berkaitan atau tidak,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}semua orang cukup khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kami ingin\Nkau memberinya bimbingan individu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku punya masa lalu dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ikatan yang lebih dalam dari laut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Judulnya "Under the Sea".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang juga begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang punya masa lalu\Nyang tidak ingin mereka bicarakan, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau menyunting adeganmu yang kacau\Nmenjadi kilas balik?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan setiap adegan ada kau,\Nkarakter utama, "Under the She"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, aku bisa mengerti kenapa kau ragu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga punya masa lalu dengannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ikatan yang lebih dalam dari laut.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kaguya…\N- Lelucon staf tadi sudah keterlaluan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka memintaku mengisi suara Takasugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang akan ingat ikatan semacam itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku malah membuat para penggemar marah
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan mendapat lebih banyak keluhan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluhan pemirsa adalah provokasi lain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuserahkan Takasugi kepadamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika hasilnya bagus,\Nkau akan diberi hadiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hasil yang bagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika, setelah bimbingan yang rajin,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}murid itu memilih jalan yang berbeda,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kurasa itu juga tidak bisa dihindari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ingin aku memaksanya putus sekolah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan itu maksudku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu maksudmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setidaknya sekitar setengahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bicara tanpa henti.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu membuat Under the Sea putraku meluap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya,\Nsemua akan berjalan sesuai rencanaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berdua sama saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berdua…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ginpachi Sakata selalu membuatku pusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membiarkan mereka\Nsaling membunuh dan menghilang bersama
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukan hal buruk bagi sekolah kita, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar-benar luar biasa…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya ingin menghancurkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hancurkan yang buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya kau diprovokasi,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepala Sekolah Bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sebut aku bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah lama di toilet, Zura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau makan sendirian?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bukan Zura, aku Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak makan sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tampak berbeda dari biasanya, serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak, kau mengerti, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan dengan ikatan kita,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau tidak bisa terus menyusahkan\Nsemua orang di Kelas Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pergi ke Starbucks\Ndengan teman lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita juga bisa menyelesaikan PR bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takasugi bukan tipe pria baik\Nyang mau mengerjakan PR denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, murid norak sepertimu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tak cocok di Starbucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini medan perang citra untuk memberikan\Nkesan bahwa "tempatku di sini".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Starbucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Frappuccino karamel yang menandakan\Nhasrat membesar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak, kau mau ikut?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mau pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penuh dengan ekspresi diri hingga\Nsatu teguk membuat orang ingin muntah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan lakukan hal yang tidak perlu\Ndan langsung pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kerjakan PR-mu,\Nsikat gigi, mandi, dan tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa pekan depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Matako, ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini perintah Pak Shinsuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cari orang yang dipaksa membeli stiker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan lihat apa kesamaan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maka kita akan tahu target pelakunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu kita akan mencari murid\Nyang mungkin menjadi target.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu kita akan tahu siapa pelakunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Stiker di tas itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu "Sangat…"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Sangat Tidak Berguna."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa dia mengiklankan\Nbahwa dia hanya makan dan tidak bekerja?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang datang lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu "Sangat…"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Sangat bagus mandi busa ini yang dimulai\Ndari 10.000 yen selama 30 menit."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa menempelkan stiker\Nyang mengiklankan tempat erotis?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang berikutnya pasti…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Sangat…"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Kau Goku atau Kakarot?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertanyaan payah macam apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:18:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hanya akan menanyakan itu\Njika tidak tahu apa-apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada satu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katsura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa menjadi percakapan\Ndengan stiker itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang ini bahkan tidak ada hubungannya\Ndengan "Sangat".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang sebenarnya ingin dia katakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak peduli!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia jelas orang terakhir di sekolah\Nyang terlibat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau membeli barang bagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kita lakukan, Senior Bansai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya itu yang bisa kau katakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar kau bertanya-tanya\Ntentang stiker itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami tidak bisa membiarkanmu\Npergi begitu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus, Semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari SMA Gintama…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takasugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Shinsuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar anak nakal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beraninya kau datang ke wilayah kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah sudah jelas?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya ingin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menghancurkan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian semua, serang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takasugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa dengannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menelepon polisi,\Njadi, jalani konseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga! Polisi datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takasugi, kau akan membayar untuk ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar-benar sudah tiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Takasugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pertemuan pertama kita di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar kau guru di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan membuatku tertawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tidak bisa mentertawakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan harus memberikan\Nbimbingan ekstrakurikuler di gang ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau berusaha membuatku dikeluarkan, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang kau menjadi pendidik yang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tidak bisa bersemangat\Njika terus begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kita tidak mengamuk
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seperti dahulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika melakukan itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita hanya akan masuk ke tangan guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil kau tidak melihat
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa yang baru saja kulakukan di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak melihat apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, aku yakin itu hanya
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}anak-anak norak minum frappuccino\Nyang menandakan hasrat membesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mendengar orang bodoh bilang\Ndia akan mengerjakan PR di Starbucks,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi, aku datang untuk melakukan\Nbimbingan individu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Langsung pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu kerjakan PR-mu,\Nsikat gigi, mandi, dan tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shinpachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedang apa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya datang\Nuntuk menyerahkan jurnal hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas kerja kerasmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga harus langsung pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pak Shinsuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti biasa, itu sangat tidak masuk akal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kita bisa menemukan\Nsesuatu yang menyenangkan di sini.
